sections.Trivia:
- In the anime version, "Toya" is changed to "Totani".
- The Detective Boys' dolls are representing characters from the Chinese tale Journey to the West:
- Genta Kojima has a doll representing Zhu Bajie;
- Ayumi Yoshida has a doll representing Tang Sanzang;
- Conan has a doll representing the Monkey King;
- Mitsuhiko has a doll representing Sha Wujing.
